---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = "July 2026";
---

<Layout
  title="Refund & Cancellation Policy – Bliss Dermacare"
  description="Bliss Dermacare's refund and cancellation policy for all services including facials, semipermanent makeup, advanced treatments, memberships, and more."
>

  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="py-14 bg-[#faf9f7] border-b border-neutral-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <span class="text-primary-600 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xs font-semibold mb-4 block">Policies & Procedures</span>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-4">Refund &amp; Cancellation Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Please read before booking. These policies reflect how we operate as a private studio and protect the quality of every client's experience.
      </p>
      <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 mt-4">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Policy Content -->
  <section class="py-14 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 space-y-12">

      <!-- Intro -->
      <div class="bg-[#faf9f7] border border-neutral-200 rounded-2xl p-7">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-3">A Word Before We Begin</h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
          Bliss Dermacare is a private, appointment-only studio in Tampa, FL. Every slot on our calendar is held exclusively for one client — which means a late cancellation or no-show has a real, direct impact on our business. Like virtually every licensed aesthetics studio, medspa, and PMU artist in the Greater Tampa Bay area — from Wesley Chapel to Land O' Lakes to New Tampa — we do not offer refunds on services that have been rendered. This is standard across the industry and exists for good reason.
        </p>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mt-3">
          That said, we are not a faceless corporation. If something genuinely goes wrong on our end, we will make it right. We just ask that you communicate with us directly — not through a chargeback.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- THE CORE RULE -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-1">The Core Rule</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-5">Applies to every service we offer.</p>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex gap-4 bg-rose-50 border border-rose-100 rounded-xl p-5">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-rose-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
            <p class="text-neutral-800 text-sm leading-relaxed"><strong>No refunds on completed services — ever.</strong> Once a treatment has been performed, the fee is final. Results vary from person to person based on skin type, health, hormones, lifestyle, and aftercare. Dissatisfaction with how results look or how long they last is not grounds for a refund.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4 bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-100 rounded-xl p-5">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            <p class="text-neutral-800 text-sm leading-relaxed"><strong>Have a genuine concern? Reach out within 48 hours.</strong> We want every client to leave happy. If something went wrong that was within our control, contact us within 48 hours of your appointment. We'll review the situation and, where appropriate, schedule a complimentary corrective follow-up. This is not a guarantee of a redo — it's a conversation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CANCELLATIONS -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-1">Cancellations &amp; No-Shows</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-5">Life happens — just communicate with us.</p>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 overflow-hidden divide-y divide-neutral-100">
          <div class="flex gap-4 p-5">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 text-sm">24+ hours notice — no charge</p>
              <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mt-1">Cancel or reschedule at least 24 hours before your appointment and there is no fee. Any deposit paid will roll over to your rescheduled visit.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4 p-5 bg-amber-50/50">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 text-sm">Under 24 hours — 50% late cancellation fee</p>
              <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mt-1">If you cancel within 24 hours of your appointment, 50% of the scheduled service price will be charged. This reflects the time that was held and cannot be filled on short notice.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4 p-5 bg-rose-50/50">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-rose-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 text-sm">No-show — 100% charge + prepayment required going forward</p>
              <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mt-1">If you do not arrive and give no notice, you will be charged the full service price. All future appointments must be paid in full at the time of booking.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4 p-5 bg-rose-50/50">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-rose-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 text-sm">Repeated cancellations — prepayment required</p>
              <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mt-1">Two or more late cancellations or no-shows within a 6-month window means all future bookings require prepayment in full, no exceptions.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- DEPOSITS -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-1">Booking Deposits</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-5">Required for select services and all new clients for high-ticket bookings.</p>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-rose-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm"><strong class="text-neutral-900">Deposits are non-refundable.</strong> A deposit secures your slot. If you cancel for any reason, the deposit is forfeited — that time was pulled from our available schedule the moment you booked.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm"><strong class="text-neutral-900">Rescheduled with 24+ hours notice?</strong> Your deposit carries forward and applies to the rescheduled appointment. Deposits may only be transferred to one new appointment date.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FACIALS -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-1">Facials</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-5">Signature Radiance · Dermaplane Glow · Smooth Canvas · Brightening Peel · Vampire Facial · Diamond Glow · Enzyme Facials · High Frequency · and all others.</p>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-rose-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm"><strong class="text-neutral-900">No refunds once the service is complete.</strong> Every facial is customized to your skin on that specific day. Reactions, purging after exfoliation treatments, and temporary redness are normal parts of the process — not service failures.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm"><strong class="text-neutral-900">Disclose everything at intake.</strong> If you have active skin conditions, recent cosmetic procedures, medications (especially retinoids or Accutane), or known sensitivities — tell us before we start. Withholding this and then experiencing a reaction is not grounds for a refund.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm"><strong class="text-neutral-900">Vampire Facial (PRP)</strong> requires a brief health screening. No refunds once the blood draw has been performed, as biological material cannot be recollected.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- LASH BROW BODY -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-1">Lash, Brow &amp; Body Services</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-5">Lash Extensions · Lash Lift & Brow Lamination · Body & Face Waxing · Brazilian Wax.</p>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-rose-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm"><strong class="text-neutral-900">No refunds on completed services.</strong> This includes full lash sets, lash lift and brow lamination, and all waxing services.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm"><strong class="text-neutral-900">Lash extensions — fill schedule matters.</strong> Longevity depends on your natural lash cycle and how consistently you maintain fills. If you wait too long between appointments and a fill isn't possible, a new full set is required at the full price. No credit for skipped fills.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm"><strong class="text-neutral-900">Allergic reaction to lash adhesive?</strong> Contact us within 24–48 hours and we will remove the extensions at no charge. If you have a known history of sensitivities, request a patch test before booking.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-rose-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm"><strong class="text-neutral-900">Waxing age restriction enforced.</strong> All waxing (body, face, Brazilian) requires clients to be 21 or older. If you arrive and don't meet this requirement, the appointment will be declined and the deposit forfeited.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- SPRAY TAN -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-1">Custom Airbrush Spray Tan</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-5">Results are heavily dependent on client preparation and aftercare — not just application.</p>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-rose-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm"><strong class="text-neutral-900">No refunds for uneven results caused by prep or aftercare.</strong> A spray tan's finish is directly affected by exfoliation done beforehand, products applied after the tan, and how quickly you showered. If you didn't follow the prep and aftercare instructions we provide, the result is not our responsibility.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm"><strong class="text-neutral-900">If we made an application error</strong> — contact us within 24 hours with photos. We will correct it at no charge while the tan can still be blended.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- SPMU -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-1">Semipermanent Makeup</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-5">Nano Brows · Powder Brows · Lip Blush · Lip Neutralization · Scalp Micropigmentation · Custom SPMU.</p>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-rose-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm"><strong class="text-neutral-900">No refunds — period.</strong> PMU is a multi-session, biology-dependent process. What you see immediately after the procedure is not the final result. Pigment will appear darker and more saturated for the first 1–2 weeks, then soften significantly during the 4–6 week healing period. Requesting a refund based on results before healing is complete is not something we accommodate — this is the standard position of every reputable PMU artist in the Tampa Bay area.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm"><strong class="text-neutral-900">Touch-up is included and must be scheduled.</strong> A complimentary perfecting touch-up is included with every initial PMU service and must be booked between 6–8 weeks post-procedure. This is when shape, color saturation, and symmetry refinements are made. Missing this window forfeits the included touch-up. Requests outside the 6–8 week range are billed at the standard touch-up rate.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm"><strong class="text-neutral-900">Retention is not guaranteed.</strong> Oily skin, prior PMU work, sun exposure, skincare actives (retinol, AHAs), certain medications, and immune response all affect how pigment holds. These known variables are discussed at consultation — they are not service defects.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm"><strong class="text-neutral-900">Scalp Micropigmentation</strong> typically requires 2–3 sessions. Each session is billed separately. No refund on completed sessions if you discontinue mid-series.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm"><strong class="text-neutral-900">Custom SPMU</strong> is priced after consultation. Once agreed upon and work begins, the quoted price is final. If you change your mind mid-session, the portion completed is charged in full.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ADVANCED TREATMENTS -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-1">Advanced Treatments &amp; Injectables</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-5">PRP · Lip Filler · ED Injectables · Collagen Induction Therapy (Microneedling) · GLP-1 Weight Loss Program.</p>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-rose-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm"><strong class="text-neutral-900">No refunds on any injectable or advanced procedure once administered.</strong> These are medical-grade interventions. Once a procedure begins, no refund will be issued — including for results that differ from expectations. Individual biological response is inherently variable and outside our control.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm"><strong class="text-neutral-900">Contraindicated at consultation?</strong> If a health screening determines we cannot safely proceed, your deposit will be fully refunded. That is the only scenario in which a refund applies to this category.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm"><strong class="text-neutral-900">Collagen Induction Therapy (Microneedling)</strong> produces progressive results across 3–6 sessions. No refund if you discontinue after your first session — single-session results will be less dramatic than the full series and this is disclosed at consultation.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-rose-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm"><strong class="text-neutral-900">GLP-1 / Weight Loss Program ($299/mo)</strong> — once a monthly cycle begins, that month's fee is non-refundable. To discontinue, contact us before your next billing date and you won't be charged going forward. The current cycle is not prorated or refunded.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ANCILLARY -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-1">Ancillary &amp; Clinical Services</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-5">IV Hydration Therapy · Personalized Lab Collection · Hormone Lab Panel · Regenerative Blood-Based Services.</p>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-rose-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm"><strong class="text-neutral-900">No refunds on completed clinical services.</strong> IV drips, lab draws, and hormone panels involve consumable supplies, professional time, and processing costs that cannot be recovered after the service begins.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm"><strong class="text-neutral-900">IV drip stopped mid-session.</strong> If you need to stop before the drip is complete, the full session fee applies. Partial sessions are not prorated.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm"><strong class="text-neutral-900">Contraindicated before we begin?</strong> If a screening reveals the service isn't safe to proceed with, your deposit will be fully refunded.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- PACKAGES -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-1">Seasonal Packages</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-5">Bronze &amp; Bare Glow · Lash &amp; Body Smooth · Brow, Lash &amp; Wax Ritual · Glow &amp; Smooth Escape · Mix &amp; Match Escape.</p>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-rose-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm"><strong class="text-neutral-900">Packages are non-refundable once booked.</strong> The bundle price is non-refundable whether or not you use both services in the package.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-rose-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm"><strong class="text-neutral-900">Packages cannot be split across visits.</strong> Both services must be received in the same appointment. If you leave before both are complete, the full package fee still applies and no credit is given for the unused portion.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm"><strong class="text-neutral-900">Late cancellation of a package.</strong> The standard 24-hour policy applies. Fees are calculated on the full package price, not the individual service price.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm"><strong class="text-neutral-900">Age requirements apply within packages.</strong> Packages that include waxing require all clients to be 21+. If this isn't met, the waxing portion is declined and the full package price is still due — the discount was for the bundle, not individual services.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- MEMBERSHIPS -->
      <div>
